Saturday 4, February 2017

2 to 5 p.m.&amp;nbsp;

&amp;nbsp;

Join us at a reception for our featured artist for February, Helen Wilkinson. 

Wilkinson said, &amp;quot;My LOVE for glass started in about 1971 when I decided I wanted a Tiffany Style lamp. I couldn&amp;#39;t afford one so I took a 6-week class in stained glass and that was the beginning &amp;mdash; and I haven&amp;#39;t stopped loving glass yet.&amp;quot;

This versatile artist creates both ornamental and functional pieces. Some are fashioned from stained glass and others from layers of glass fused together, forming patterns or designs depending on colors or other materials used.&amp;nbsp; Her jewelry utilizes crystals, pearls, her lamp-work beads, and colorful fused glass. Helen takes orders for her stained glass wall hangings, sun catchers and automobile designs.&amp;nbsp;

Meet Helen and view her creative and colorful designs.&amp;nbsp;

Sutter Creek Gallery

35 Main Street

Sutter Creek, CA 95685

209-267-0228

suttercreekgallery@gmail.com

www.suttercreekgallery.com/

