The St. George Historic Hotel is located in Volcano-the &amp;ldquo;Gem of the Mother Lode&amp;rdquo;, slightly off the beaten path in the Sierra Nevada Foothills of California.&amp;nbsp; The 3-story building with wooden balconies is the first thing you&amp;rsquo;ll see upon approaching the entrance to town.

