EVENT DATE:&amp;nbsp; March 25, 2017&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;8:00 am &amp;ndash; 2:00 pm

&amp;nbsp;

►► January 30 &amp;ndash; Registration begins

&amp;nbsp;

►► DEADLINE TO REGISTER: March 6 (no exceptions)

&amp;nbsp;

LOCATION: Amador High School, Sutter Creek, 330 Spanish St.

