&amp;nbsp;

The Pumpkin Contest promises to be bigger than ever!&amp;nbsp; Pumpkin registration 9am to noon on Buena Vista Street.Giant pumpkin prizes: 1st place 18 &amp;amp; over - $1,000. 1st place 17 &amp;amp; under - $500. Cash prizes to 5th place.

