&amp;nbsp;

The Scarecrow Contest has many ways to participate: classrooms, kids, adults or groups.Classrooms build their scarecrow in advance, and it will be delivered for judging the day of the Harvest Faire. Individuals build their own scarecrows starting at 9 a.m. and compete for cash prizes.Scarecrows will be on display throughout downtown Ione through Halloween. Prizes awarded at 2:30.

