Annually

1st Saturday, December

9:30am-1:00pm

&amp;nbsp;

Unique Art by Unique People -&amp;nbsp;A program where artists with Developmental Disabilities create, exhibit &amp;amp; sell art.

&amp;nbsp;

The Arc of Amador and Calaveras is hosting its annual ArCreations Art Show and Sale along with its annual Holiday Raffle.

&amp;nbsp;

The Arc provides quality programs and services to over 200 intellectually and developmentally disabled adults in Amador and Calaveras Counties.

&amp;nbsp;

The artwork sold at ArCreations is made throughout the year by Arc clients and consists of birdhouses, fine ar,t photography, jewelry, knick knacks, baked goods, planter boxes and more.

&amp;nbsp;

The commission the artists receive allows them to buy special items during the Holidays, and the artwork makes great gifts for loved ones on the shopping list.

&amp;nbsp;

Refreshments are available throughout the event along with live music featuring Arc Performers.&amp;nbsp; Raffle at1:00pm.

