6:00 pm

&amp;nbsp;

Las Posadas Candlelight Walk reenacts Joseph&amp;#39;s and Mary&amp;rsquo;s journey to Bethlehem. 

&amp;nbsp;

The&amp;nbsp;walk starts at Immaculate Conception Catholic Church on Spanish Street in Sutter Creek. Mary and Joseph proceed down historic Spanish Street, lined with flickering luminaria and onto Main Street. As they go from inn to inn looking for shelter, narrators retell the familiar story and musicians lead all&amp;nbsp;followers in familiar Christmas carols.

&amp;nbsp;

A heart warming experience for all ages, the Las Posadas Candlelight Walk will be an evening you will cherish. Dress warmly so you can enjoy the entire evening.

