Annually

Last Friday

of January

&amp;nbsp;

January 27, 2017

&amp;nbsp;

Doors Open 5:30PM

Dinner 6:30PM

&amp;nbsp;

Annual Spaghetti Feed Dinner includes salad, hot parmesan bread, meaty red sauce spaghetti and green pesto spaghetti, as well as dessert.&amp;nbsp; 

Wine, soft drinks and water&amp;nbsp; available for purchase.&amp;nbsp; 

&amp;nbsp;

Lots of great raffle prizes, too.

Tickets $20 per person, $25 per person at the door. 

Tickets 209-223-6349

All proceeds benefit our Amador County Historic Cemetaries

Italian Picnic Grounds

581 State Highway 49

Sutter Creek, CA&amp;nbsp; 95685

