&amp;nbsp;

4th Saturday

January 28th

5:30pm

&amp;nbsp;

Join Andis Wines&amp;nbsp;in the Barrel Room for&amp;nbsp;the Annual Crab Feed and White Wines Release Party.

&amp;nbsp;

Be the first to taste brand new releases of Sauvignon Blanc, Semillon and Chenin Blanc.

&amp;nbsp;

Enjoy an all-you-can-eat dinner complete with fresh bread, Caesar salad, pasta chuta and fresh Dungeness crab courtesy of Rudy&amp;#39;s Hideaway. Discover how perfectly our white wines pair with fresh seafood, there&amp;#39;s nothing quite like it!

&amp;nbsp;

Tickets /Wine club members (must login to receive discount online)

&amp;nbsp;

RSVP required. Seating is limited. Don&amp;#39;t forget your crab forks and butter burners.

&amp;nbsp;

More Info:&amp;nbsp; andiswines.com/News-Events

Contact:&amp;nbsp; Jenae Plasse (209)245-6177,&amp;nbsp; jenae@andiswines.com

&amp;nbsp;

Andis Wines Barrel Room
11000 Shenandoah Road

Plymouth CA&amp;nbsp; 95669

